    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 13th level, you can weave a veil of psychic static to mask yourself. As an action, you can magically become invisible, along with anything you are wearing or carrying, for 1 hour or until you dismiss this effect (no action required). This invisibility ends early immediately after you deal damage to a creature or you force a creature to make a saving throw.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you cannot do so again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a Psionic Energy die to use this feature again.</p>",
